	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002020_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<!--Hand 01 39 top left--><!--Hand 02 64759 top right-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">His Excellency</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="center">Sir Bartle Frere</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">The Governor</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Bombay</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Livingstone</p>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002020_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<!--Hand 01 39 top left--><!--Hand 02 64759 top right-->
				<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><term type="boat">Lady of Nyassa</term></p>
				<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><placeName>Bombay Harbour</placeName></p>
				<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>14 June 1864</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p><persName>Sir</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I send herewith a 
<lb/>letter from His Highness the 
<lb/><persName>Sultan of Zanzibar</persName>
<lb/>which he entrusted to 
<lb/>my care, and I regret 
<lb/>that owing to our 
<lb/>being becalmed 24 <unclear cert="low">1/2</unclear>
<lb/>days and having but 
<lb/>one stoker to manage 
<lb/>the engines and he 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002020_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<lb/>laid up a good while 
<lb/>by illness, it has been 
<lb/>delayed by a passage 
<lb/>of forty four days. A 
<lb/>small mail 
<w>accom-<lb break="no"/>panies</w> it.</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I have &amp;c. &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">David Livingstone</p>
<lb/>
<lb/>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">To</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Sir Bartle Frere</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">&amp;c &amp;c.</p>
			
